@startuml
title Cloud Function State Transitions

[*] --> Queued : Event arrives in Cloud Storage

Queued --> Processing : Cloud Function Triggered
Processing --> WaitingForTMS : Send Event to TMS Bridge
WaitingForTMS --> Processing : Response Received
Processing --> Success : Publish Processed Data

WaitingForTMS --> Retry : Timeout or Error
Retry --> Processing : Retry Processing
Retry --> Failed : Max Retries Reached

Success --> [*]
Failed --> [*]

@enduml